channel.title: Need help trying to download flash file
channel.description:
Well I was surfing around the web and I happened to come across this awesome virtual "fish tank" that could be used as a desktop background or even as a screensaver. I had tried to use IE's caching system to retrieve the cached files but the .swf file does not work meaning the "fish tank" would not load even though I had gotten all the files. The link to the webpage is here: [url=http://www.papervision3d.org/]http://www.papervision3d.org/[/url]
If anyone can attach the working swf file with the image and script files that will be much appreciated. Thanks.
